---
title: Quick Crumbed Chicken & Lemony Bacon Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt & Slivered Almonds
description: A golden and crunchy crumb on chicken is the only way to go. It matches the bright and sunny couscous, tossed with bacon bits, roast veggies and there’s a zap of zest in this bowl too. Everything is shining and golden tonight!
